    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1867-09-23T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1867-09-23T00:00:00-05:00" n="149" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d149">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Adams</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                                Seward</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 1457.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,
                                        <hi rend="italic">London,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1867-09-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">September</hi> 23, 1867</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi> I have received information that Colonels
                            Nagle and Warren have been transferred from Kilmainham jail, where they
                            have been exposed to the rather <pb facs="0220" n="152" xml:id="pg_152"/> severe discipline of that local prison, to Mountjoy, which is more
                            directly under the supervision of the government.</p>
                <p>The reason assigned for the delay in an answer to my application for
                            their release is, that the Irish attorney general has not yet returned
                            from a brief absence.</p>
                <p>I have the honor to be, sir, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>CHARLES FRANCIS ADAMS,</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">William H. Seward,</hi>
                        <hi rend="italic">Secretary of State, Washington, D.C.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
